<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我之前<delay20 />跟你說過
想要離開這座島的事，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但後來<delay8 />我放棄那個念頭了──！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />老實說，<delay20 />
後來跟<tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />討論了一下，<delay20 />
我突然覺得搬不搬都無所謂了，<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且最重要的是，<delay20 />
我們兩個<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都還沒有<delay8 />分出勝負！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以啦，<delay8 />今後也請多多指教──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我<delay8 />之前曾經說過要離開這座島，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但後來<delay8 />我放棄那個念頭了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />後來<delay20 /><tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" /><delay8 />挽留了我，<delay frames="40" />
所以我<delay8 />改變心意了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是這麼一回事啦，<delay20 />從今以後<delay8 />
我們也繼續當好朋友吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實<delay20 />是前陣子<delay20 />我跟你說要搬家的那件事啦。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我放棄<delay8 />那個念頭了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我那天和你談過之後，<delay8 />
又和<tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />討論了很多事情<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那時候我才清楚地明白到，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />果然這座島才是<delay8 />我的歸宿啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是這麼一回事，<delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從今以後也請你多多指教啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />前陣子不是跟你說過
我想離開這座島嗎？<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請你把<delay8 />那件事忘了吧──！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />後來我仔細想了想，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才發現<delay8 />自己還是非常喜歡<delay20 />這座島的！<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且最重要的是<delay20 />
我還沒有跟你分出勝負啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以啦，<delay8 />今後也請多多指教──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
